This is a **favorite interview question**. With this questions, the interviewer tries to find out how well you understand the behavior of objects with respect to constructors, methods, class variables (static variables) and instance variables.&lt;br&gt;
Now a days interviewers are asking another favorite question **what is effectively final** from java 1.8.&lt;br&gt; I will explain in the end about this `effectively final` in java 1.8.

    import java.util.ArrayList;
    import java.util.List;
    
    class Test {
    	private final List foo;
    
    	public Test() {
    		foo = new ArrayList();
